300
00:11:10.730 --> 00:11:13.690
al palacio de cristal para interrogar cuanto antes

301
00:11:13.690 --> 00:11:14.810
a Zametov.

302
00:11:15.930 --> 00:11:16.890
Raskolnikov

303
00:11:16.890 --> 00:11:18.570
